{"tid":1296150,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"深圳市體育中心拆卸期間倒塌　至少6人傷","createTime":"2019-07-08T09:27:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T00:46:35.000Z","uid":141151,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"abbb945ed0a4bda0f046097a5e063af504375172","tid":1296150,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T09:27:04.000Z","msg":"深圳市體育中心拆卸期間倒塌 至少6人傷<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1467211-20190708.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1467211-20190708.htm&d=ng3vG9SJ7BvQZwuOeCzNpYVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=e05efb9e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1467211-20190708.htm&h=11864ce4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1467211-20190708.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n深圳市體育中心在清拆過程中倒塌，至少6人受傷，估計仍然有2名工人被埋。<br />\n<br />\n事發在上午大約11時半，倒塌的是位於福田區深圳市體育中心的體育館籃球館部分，深圳公安、應急消防等部門趕到現場，將一度被困的傷者抬上擔架送院。救援工作仍正進行，事故原因有待進一步調查。<br />\n<br />\n體育中心目前仍在進行翻新重建，預計明年中完工。館裡所有商鋪清空，倒塌前只剩下部分支撐柱，周邊亦完成基本清拆。"},{"pid":"274a0e70234c256381baea3f58e8bd690fc84bf3","tid":1296150,"uid":215634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T09:45:16.000Z","msg":"拆完再起，GDP up up up！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5f31f7cebb53e7c106e5cf48476c4001a6374ca","tid":1296150,"uid":32675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T09:57:17.000Z","msg":"醫院同墳場又有生意,GDP又升,中国或成最大驘家"},{"pid":"c14dde6e6e42ad98705f5ae11d603fd245647845","tid":1296150,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:27:04.000Z","msg":"多難興邦"},{"pid":"a037667a51596ee1769da148659c516e55b50751","tid":1296150,"uid":4462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:34:44.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">抵撚死</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"1ded4ad435eae873dd11aaf39e9c67ae7c648a33","tid":1296150,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T00:46:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}